The content presented in this repository are distributed under the following
conditions:

1. Translations of the documentation texts of the Editor Vim program under the
   terms of an Open Publication License.
   The text of this license is presented in the file "LICENSE-OPL.md"
2. Translations of menus and messages of the Editor Vim program and other files
   and accompanying documents supplied to the RuVim translation package under
   the terms of the Vim License.
   The text of this license is presented in the file "LICENSE-VL.md"

The copyrights of the source texts in English of the documentation of the Editor
Vim program, the menu and message files of the Editor Vim program belong to
their owner.
The copyright for translations of the documentation of the Editor Vim program,
menu files and messages of the Editor Vim program belong to their authors.
The contact details of the authors of the translations are specified in the
source texts of these translations.
Registered trademarks and patent names found both in English texts and in
translations into Russian belong to their owners.


